---
import { siteConfig } from "../config";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anek+Devanagari:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <title>FAQ</title>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-white text-gray-800">

    <section class="px-6 sm:px-10 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 overflow-x-hidden">

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-20 items-start">

        <!-- LEFT -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">

          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-7xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            Frequently Asked Questions.
          </h2>

          <div
            class="w-[75px] h-[5px] mt-2 rounded-full"
            style={`background-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}
          ></div>

          <p class="text-gray-500 mt-5 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-sm leading-relaxed">
            Quick answers about services, timelines, and how I work.
          </p>

        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 w-full min-w-0">

          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl 
                      p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12
                      shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300
                      w-full max-w-full">

            <div class="space-y-8 text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            
              <!-- 1 -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  1. Can you match my style or reference?
                </h2>
            
                <p>
                  Yes. You can share references, examples, or even rough ideas. I’ll adapt the design style to match your vision while improving it for better results.
                </p>
              </div>
            
              <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-300 to-transparent"></div>
            
              <!-- 2 -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  2. What if I don’t know exactly what I want?
                </h2>
            
                <p>
                  No problem. Share your goal and I’ll help shape it into a clear creative direction with examples and recommendations.
                </p>
              </div>
            
              <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-300 to-transparent"></div>
            
              <!-- 3 -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  3. Do you work with creators, brands, or businesses?
                </h2>
            
                <p>
                  I work with creators, founders, and businesses—from one-off assets to ongoing content systems.
                </p>
              </div>
            
              <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-300 to-transparent"></div>
            
              <!-- 4 -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  4. Can you handle ongoing or monthly work?
                </h2>
            
                <p>
                  Yes. I offer continuous design and editing support for clients who need regular content like social media, videos, or branding updates.
                </p>
              </div>
            
              <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-300 to-transparent"></div>
            
              <!-- 5 -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  5. How fast can you deliver?
                </h2>
            
                <p>
                  Turnaround depends on scope. Small tasks are often delivered within 24–48 hours, while larger projects follow a phased timeline.
                </p>
              </div>
            
              <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-300 to-transparent"></div>
            
              <!-- 6 -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  6. What happens after I submit the form?
                </h2>
            
                <p>
                  I’ll reply with scope, timeline, pricing, and next steps. Once approved, I begin production.
                </p>
              </div>
            
              <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-300 to-transparent"></div>
            
              <!-- 7 -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  7. Will I see previews before final delivery?
                </h2>
            
                <p>
                  Yes. You’ll receive previews or drafts for feedback before final files are delivered.
                </p>
              </div>
            
              <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-300 to-transparent"></div>
            
              <!-- 8 -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  8. What if I need changes after delivery?
                </h2>
            
                <p>
                  Minor revisions are included. Additional revisions can be added based on scope and timeline.
                </p>
              </div>
            
              <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-300 to-transparent"></div>
            
              <!-- 9 -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  9. Do you work with international clients?
                </h2>
            
                <p>
                  Yes. I work with clients worldwide and manage communication online for a smooth workflow.
                </p>
              </div>
            
              <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-300 to-transparent"></div>
            
              <!-- 10 -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  10. Why work with me?
                </h2>
            
                <p>
                  I focus on practical creative work that supports measurable goals, not just aesthetics. You get clear communication, reliable execution, and detail-focused output.
                </p>
              </div>
            
              <!-- CONTACT -->
              <div class="pt-8">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-base sm:text-lg">
                  Still have questions?
                </p>
            
                <p class="text-gray-900 font-medium mt-1">
                  {siteConfig.social.email}
                </p>
            
              </div>
            
            </div>

          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

    </section>

  </body>
</html>
